Cell["\<\
We expand the numerical solution using only this axial field and plot the two \
fields near the optic-axis:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9815338706717453`*^9, 
  3.981533920418642*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d71eb6dc-dc6e-4ed2-881b-\
